    - target: {fileID: 1496233484427879800, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: Wilma Kainde
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1496233484427879800, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_StaticEditorFlags
      value: 2147483647
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2551726049934924149, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_StaticEditorFlags
      value: 2147483647
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2643042366593121615, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueParagraphs.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2643042366593121615, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueParagraphs.Array.data[0]'
      value: Halo, selamat datang di Kantor FILKOM! Saya Wilma Kainde, Sekretaris
        Fakultas. Jika butuh informasi, bantuan administrasi, atau ingin bertemu
        Pak Dekan dan para Kaprodi, di sinilah pusatnya.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2643042366593121615, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueParagraphs.Array.data[1]'
      value: Ruangannya nyaman, kan? Jangan sungkan bertanya kalau bingung mencari
        meja siapa. Saya siap membantu!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2643042366593121615, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueParagraphs.Array.data[2]'
      value: Bagaimana? Ruangannya cukup nyaman, kan? Jangan sungkan untuk bertanya
        kalau kamu bingung mencari meja siapa. Saya di sini untuk membantu!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2946687659806495174, guid: 95f8b2441b30ae64798b9c4dd4e3e968, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_StaticEditorFlags
      value: 2147483647
